metadata.name: GENESIS Pass
metadata.description:
This pass can be burned at any time in exchange for a $99 gift card to NFTCanvases.com.

GENESIS Passholders receive the following benefits on NFTCanvases.com:

-10% Lifetime discount on prints  
-1.5x Bonus on commissions in our seller marketplace coming in Q1 2023, allowing users to monetize their NFTs by selling limited print editions in our curated gallery  
-5 FREE prints per month will be gifted to Genesis Passholders at random each month  
-Notifications of exclusive print drops prior to release
